{"tid":2292430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【準備緊】新國防部長Miller︰所有特種作戰部隊直接歸我管轄","createTime":"2020-11-19T13:08:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T18:34:06.000Z","uid":154486,"like":110,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"029bc914e77d5bf9da81596bf7c48b14c41bb678","tid":2292430,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T13:08:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/M2Madness/status/1329071464230789123?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FM2Madness%2Fstatus%2F1329071464230789123%3Fs%3D19&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopXXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=569e663d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FM2Madness%2Fstatus%2F1329071464230789123%3Fs%3D19&h=4070b2c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/M2Madness/status/1329071464230789123?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;This reform will immediately improve agility to the department and the command and will enable us to streamline the information flow, enhance decision-making and more adaptively and adeptly support our commanders and their superb soldiers, sailors, airmen and Marines,&rdquo;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n跳過舊程序直接歸Miller管轄<br />\n姐係可以話所有特種部隊都直接由侵指揮<br />\n<br />\n呢個改革已經講左3年<br />\n過左國會，而家先正式實行<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_Defense_Authorization_Act_for_Fiscal_Year_2017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FNational_Defense_Authorization_Act_for_Fiscal_Year_2017&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopXXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=d5883bd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_Defense_Authorization_Act_for_Fiscal_Year_2017</a><br />\n<br />\n報道：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.militarytimes.com/news/your-military/2020/11/18/pentagon-shakeup-means-more-civilian-oversight-for-special-operations/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.militarytimes.com%2Fnews%2Fyour-military